{"tid":1935408,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對於利用地區小型工程計劃興建「音樂噴泉」的建議","createTime":"2020-03-20T14:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T14:08:23.000Z","uid":343184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4f861f6a60adbb6af5c7ffa784bdcd1f5cc8e004","tid":1935408,"uid":343184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">對於利用地區小型工程計劃興建「連儂牆」的建議，民政處指，項目可能影響社區秩序或引發衝突，「我們認為不符合地區小型工程計劃」的目的；民政處又指，區議會興建「連儂牆」並不符合現行有關告示牌的政策，即展示與區議會有關資料的作用，亦可能影響社區秩序或引發衝突等，不應進行</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對於利用地區小型工程計劃興建「<span style=\"color: gold;\">音樂噴泉</span>」的建議，<span style=\"color: gold;\">眾連登仔</span>指，項目可能影響社區秩序或引發衝突，「我們認為不符合地區小型工程計劃」的目的；<span style=\"color: gold;\">連登仔</span>又指，區議會興建「<span style=\"color: gold;\">音樂噴泉</span>」並不符合現行有關<span style=\"color: gold;\">噴泉</span>的政策，即符合<span style=\"color: gold;\">市民期望的休憩場所</span>的作用，亦可能影響社區秩序或引發<span style=\"color: gold;\">汽油彈</span>等，不應進行。</span><br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E8%99%95-%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86-%E6%88%96%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E8%2599%2595-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%258